Class SafrasAlgorithm.STVCheckForFinalSucc

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2dstar.SafrasAlgorithm.STVCheckForFinalSucc
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SafrasAlgorithm.SafraTreeVisitor
    Enclosing class:
    SafrasAlgorithm

    public class SafrasAlgorithm.STVCheckForFinalSucc
extends java.lang.Object
implements SafrasAlgorithm.SafraTreeVisitor
    A Safra tree visitor that checks if all the successor states in the NBA of the label are accepting. If this is the case, all children are removed, and the final flag is set.
